title: Enticed
description: Destry and Emma are destined souls, meant to be together, but the Dark Ones are determined to tear them apart. Something evil is lurking in the shadows, and Emma must find a way to defeat the demons who threaten to take away the boy she loves or lose him forever. But she can't do it alone. The powers of Heaven take on the angels of Hell in this last chapter of the Eternal series, and there can only be one winner.
author: Chantelle Nay
